sentences.sContent: I can name quite a few of these but one of the more sensitive conditions is female incontinence.
sentences.sCn: 我能说出相当多疾病的名字而其中一个比较敏感的就是女性尿失禁。

sentences.sContent: I personally know quite a few intelligent people who (in certain situations and circumstances) can be kinda stupid. I'm know 'cause I'm one of them!
sentences.sCn: 我个人知道相当多的一些有才智的人，在某些情况和场景下，是有一些愚蠢，因为我也是其中之一。

trans.tranCn: 相当多；不少(后接可数名词)
